EmailTemplate.name: MX Thank You
EmailTemplate.subject: Thank You!
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Hi Everyone!
Can you believe it's been almost a full week since you left Mexico? I hope you are adjusting well to life back in Canada, have had some time to reflect on your trip and are enjoying your life back home with a whole new perspective.
Although I wasn't in Mexico with you, I have heard such great things about your group. Your staff had so many great things to say about you all and spoke highly of your hard work and dedication. Thank you!
A few reminders.....
Volunteer Hours Letter
I've attached a letter that states you have volunteered with Live Different. You are welcome to print this off and use it as confirmation of your volunteer experience.
Reference Letters
If you need a reference letter that is more specific (for example, for a scholarship), please send me an email. I'm more than happy to help with this. Even if it's months from now when you need one, please don't hesitate to ask.
Internship, Academy and Upcoming Trips
Our internship applications for next summer will be posted on our website in September and will close at the end of October. If you are interested, please apply online in September.
Our Academy will be starting September 14th,. We have one spot left! If you would like to find out more, please let me know.
We have public trips happening December 2014 in both the Dominican and Mexico. If you or anyone you know is interesting in coming, please register soon as the trips are filling up. Registration closes September 15th.
Lastly, we have opened up registration for our Haiti 2015 trip happening May 9 - 18, 2015. If you're considering coming on this trip, please call me as I'd be happy to provide you with more information.
Don't Forget!
Share your stories, print off photos, and stay connected with the new friends you have made on the trip!
Again, thank you for all of your hard work, dedication, support and commitment. Good luck on your future endeavors and know that your family here at Live Different is always just a phone call away.
Thank you!!
Jenn
